- **ðŸŽ¯ AST-Based Analysis**: Proper parsing instead of regex pattern matching
- **ðŸ”„ Recursive Conditions**: Handles nested condition groups (AND/OR/NOT)
- **ðŸ§  Function Side-Effects**: Infers field modifications from function calls
- **âš¡ Zero False Positives**: Accurate dependency detection
